quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,Ndayira ekibala ekiyitibwa Tiin n’ekibala ekiyitibwa Zaitun
  95,2,Era ndayira olusozi lw’e Sinai
  95,3,Nakino e kibuga (Makkah) eky’emirembe
  95,4,Mazima twakola omuntu mu kifaananyi e kisinga okuba ekirungi
  95,5,Ate oluvanyuma tumuzzaayo wansi mu ddaala erisembayo
  95,6,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi, bagenda kufuna e mpeera etalina kkomo"
  95,7,Bwekiba bw'ekityo (ate gwe omuntu) olimbisa otya olunaku lw'enkomerero
  95,8,Tolaba nti Katonda ye Mulamuzi asinga okuba omwenkanya era owamazima